  "rows": [
    {
      "$id": 1,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<BC3DF146>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "I thought it was eternal"
    },
    {
      "$id": 2,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<29E2C5B3>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "That this now would go on like this forever"
    },
    {
      "$id": 3,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<9EA7A1DA>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "Just as anyone would naturally think, because"
    },
    {
      "$id": 4,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<3E1374BD>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "You were always by my side"
    },
    {
      "$id": 5,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<540AF7EA>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "Without a single doubt, as if it were only natural"
    },
    {
      "$id": 6,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<E8935C18>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "I spent each day that way"
    },
    {
      "$id": 7,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<AD438F48>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "But I realized"
    },
    {
      "$id": 8,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<66DBA99C>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "It was a one-in-a-thousand miracle"
    },
    {
      "$id": 9,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<9E934427>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "Your sleeping face is there"
    },
    {
      "$id": 10,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<F0E88C21>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "Peaceful, the same you as always is there"
    },
    {
      "$id": 11,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<7438114E>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "To make this warmth I feel eternal"
    },
    {
      "$id": 12,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<84599B69>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "Let us return once more to that day"
    },
    {
      "$id": 13,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<7F63A46E>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "Along with the flow of time"
    },
    {
      "$id": 14,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<0AD86686>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "People, and the world, go on changing"
    },
    {
      "$id": 15,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<DA11858E>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "I had no time to feel it, because"
    },
    {
      "$id": 16,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<DBFAB8D2>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "You were always smiling"
    },
    {
      "$id": 17,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<7F50FF04>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "I wondered what tomorrow's you would be like"
    },
    {
      "$id": 18,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<4BE81EE2>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "I could not even imagine it"
    },
    {
      "$id": 19,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<002B947B>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "But I realized"
    },
    {
      "$id": 20,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<77B5A1C0>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "That those feelings can give birth to miracles"
    },
    {
      "$id": 21,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<1711F241>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "Your smile is there"
    },
    {
      "$id": 22,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<C30A4DA2>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "Brightly, there you are, speaking to me"
    },
    {
      "$id": 23,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<4FD205E4>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "To protect this moment, this eternal now"
    },
    {
      "$id": 24,
      "<8C7DD24D>": "<50650414>",
      "<554EE944>": 170,
      "<DBAF43F0>": "Let us return once more to that day"
    },
    {
